X11 Forwarding (For Linux/macOS users) 
If you are on Linux or macOS, you can forward the graphical display over SSH directly to your display.
Connect: Use the command: ssh -X username@vps_ip.
Launch: Type chromium-browser in the terminal. The window will open on your local computer.

